      "text": "先生ではないんだけど……。『魚魚っとさんの抱き\nまくらを発売してほしい』……これはいけそうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sensei‚ anyway… “I want them to release a\nGyoGyotto-san printed long cushion”… This one seems doable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.1666589739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
