      "text": "最近、お仕事が忙しくて、家族で過ごす時間も少なく\nなってたから、ちょうどいいかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been busy with work lately‚ and haven’t spended much time\nwith my family‚ so I thought it would be a good opportunity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.0333256406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
